reviewText: We tried twice to introduce our son to this video and it falls short of his interest. Just not up to par with the other "Kids Sing Along" videos

Watched this as a kid and I still can't get the songs out of my head. If you want your children to grow up experiencing pain and trama buy this movie....I say this from the point of that my grandma bought this when it first came out in 1991. It was cute when I was a kid....but for serious the songs still haunt me every christmas season.
